quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,By iute gallopers
  100,2,aprinde scânteia
  100,3,Invada (dusman) dimineata
  100,4,Lovi terror therein
  100,5,Patrunde inima their teritoriu
  100,6,uman exista exista unappreciative ai his Domnitor
  100,7,El urs martor acesta fact
  100,8,El iubi fizic obiect excessively
  100,9,El nu realiza ca zi veni when groapa Does descuia
  100,10,Tot secret exista aduce out
  100,11,"Ei do el gasi out, ala zi their Domnitor exista fully Cognizant ai ele"